    "We apply path minimization after collecting new path constraints from any if or while statement while traversing the focal method AST.",
    "Context ConstructionPrior work in test generation with LLMs have demonstrated that including additional context to the focal method definition is beneficial to the quality of test generations [36].",
    "For SymPrompt, we focus on exposing two types of context to the model that are beneficial to generating correct test cases: (i) Type context.",
    "Context that includes type definitions for focal method parameters guides the model to generate correct test inputs, particularly when the input involves complex data structures.",
    "(ii) Dependency Context."
